## ‚ùå Failed Test Analysis (3/20)

### **Critical Flow Failures**

1. **‚ùå Content Loading & Display** - FAILED (1.16s)
   - **Issue**: XPath selector syntax error
   - **Root Cause**: Invalid XPath expression for dashboard header detection
   - **Impact**: Core content loading functionality not verified
   - **Recommendation**: Update XPath selectors to match actual DOM structure

2. **‚ùå Content Selection & Details** - FAILED (1.03s)
   - **Issue**: No clickable content cards detected
